#Three fruits A,B,C are given in xkg,ykg and zkg.Find how many time times we can make fruit salad in 1:2:4 ratio using the given input.
import java.util.*;
public class Main
{
	public static void main(String[] args) {
	Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
	int x = sc.nextInt();
	int y = sc.nextInt();
	int  z = sc.nextInt();
	int count =0;
	while(x >=1 && y>=2 && z>=4){
	    count ++;
	    x = x - 1;
	    y = y - 2;
	    z = z - 4;
	}
	System.out.print(count);
	}
}

output:
1 2 4
2

2 5 10
2
